---
import H1 from "../components/h1.astro";
import InfoLayout from "../layouts/InfoLayout.astro";
---

<InfoLayout>
     <div class="p-4 sm:pt-8 sm:px-12 pb-20 min-h-dvh flex flex-col justify-between gap-32">
          <div class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-12">
               <H1>Bringing Your Ideas to Life with Technology. </H1>

               <p class="text-xl xl:text-2xl text-zinc-500 text-balance">
                    I believe the best technology is the one that feels effortless to users. As a full-stack developer, 
                    my primary focus is designing and building web applications that not only work seamlessly behind the scenes, 
                    but also feel fast, intuitive, and delightful to use. With expertise in the TypeScript ecosystem, 
                    I ensure every line of code I write delivers reliability and scalability at its core.
               </p>
          </div>

          <div class="w-full text-base sm:text-lg flex flex-col lg:flex-row lg:justify-between gap-8">
               <div class="space-y-2 flex-1">
                    <h2 class="px-4 text-zinc-400 underline underline-offset-4 decoration-zinc-500">Achievements</h2>

                    <ul class="px-4 text-zinc-400 list-disc list-outside">
                         <li>1st Place Software Development GENETIC USM Semarang 2025</li>
                         <li>1st Place Information System GEMASI AMIKOM 2024</li>
                         <li>TOP 50 out of 644 Products Bangkit Academy 2024 Batch 2</li>
                         <li>3rd Place Software Development ITFEST Paramadina 2025</li>
                         <li>3rd Runner-up Software Development UNITY UNY #13 2025</li>
                         <li>Qualified for GARENA GAMEJAM #2 Surabaya 2025</li>
                         <li>Participated in INTERNATIONAL Machine Learning Hackathon Malaysia</li>
                         <li>Participated in Hackfest by GOOGLE</li>
                    </ul>
               </div>

               <div class="space-y-2 flex-1">
                    <h2 class="px-4 text-zinc-400 underline underline-offset-4 decoration-zinc-500">Tech Stack</h2>
                    
                    <div class="px-4 text-zinc-400 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                         <span class="bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">TypeScript</span>
                         <span class="bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">SvelteKit</span>
                         <span class="bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">React</span>
                         <span class="bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Next.js</span>
                         <span class="bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Nuxt.js</span>
                         <span class="bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Vue</span>
                         <span class="bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Express</span>
                         <span class="bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Laravel</span>
                         <span class="bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">CodeIgniter</span>
                         <span class="bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">MySQL</span>
                         <span class="bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">PostgreSQL</span>
                         <span class="bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Docker</span>
                         <span class="bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Linux</span>
                         <span class="bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Git</span>
                         <span class="bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">RabbitMQ</span>
                         <span class="bg-zinc-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-sm">Redis</span>
                    </div>
               </div>
          </div>
     </div>
</InfoLayout>
